					<td>
					

						<div class="postbody">You would still need some way to store the modified program. This is just the standardization of a convention to link programs that run in NES RAM but can also be loaded as a ROM, much like the <a href="http://www.devrs.com/gba/files/mbv2faqs.php#Both" class="postlink">"mb.gba" convention</a> on Game Boy Advance.</div>

					
